        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Erp migration slippage, cyber incident exposure, and inconsistent copilot adoption are converging into a Technology Steering Committee in 30 days. Draft a crisp 1-page CEO briefing that explains the situation in plain language, the likely questions directors will ask first, and the 5 decisions that must be ready before the meeting opens. Present as a structured table with columns for Issue, Why It Matters, Board Question, and Recommended Answer.'},
        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'The Technology Steering Committee chair needs a verbal opening script for a high-pressure session covering the 6-month ERP delay and 14-hour service degradation. Write a 90-second opening statement that acknowledges the underperformance directly, explains why ERP migration slippage, cyber incident exposure, and inconsistent Copilot adoption matter most, and signals immediate corrective action without sounding defensive. End with 3 talking points to use if directors challenge management credibility.'},
        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Prepare a stakeholder communication map for the 6-month ERP delay and 14-hour service degradation and the upcoming Technology Steering Committee. Identify the priority audiences, the message each audience needs, the timing, and the main communication risk if the message is mishandled. Present as a RAG table with Red for immediate same-day communication needs, Amber for 24-hour needs, and Green for monitor-only audiences.'}
